        public StatsFacetResult(FieldDescriptor<T> field,
                        T min,
                        T max,
                        T sum,
                        Long count,
                        Long missing,
                        Double sumOfSquares,
                        T mean,
                        Double stddev,
                        Map<Double,Double> percentiles,
                        List<T> distinctValues,
                        Long countDistinct,
                        Long cardinality)
        Creates a new instance of StatsFacetResult.
        Parameters:
        field - FieldDescriptor of the document on which the stats are calculated.
        min - Minimum value of the field.
        max - Maximum value of the field
        sum - Summation of all values of the field. Valid when T extends Number, T extends Date, or T extends ZoneDateTime.
        count - Count of documents containing the field.
        missing - Count of documents missing the field.
        sumOfSquares - Summation of the squares of all the field values. Valid when T extends Number, T extends Date, or T extends ZoneDateTime.
        mean - Average calculation oof the field values. Valid when T extends Number, T extends Date, or T extends ZoneDateTime.
        stddev - Standard deviation of the field values. Valid when T extends Number, T extends Date, or T extends ZoneDateTime.
        percentiles - Map of percentile values for each given in query percentage of sample. Valid when T extends Number.
        distinctValues - List of distinct values on the field.
        countDistinct - Number of distinct values on the field.
        cardinality - Statistical approximation to the number of different values on the field.
